title: Zojirushi Micom Rice Cooker & Warmer NS-TSC10/18
description:
This multi-cooker includes a steamer basket and steam setting to cook much more than perfect rice. Steam a salmon steak while cooking rice, or use it as a steamer to steam dim sum. The Zojirushi Micom Rice Cooker & Warmer (NS-TSC10/18) also comes with a cake setting. Yes, you can even bake a cake! The brushed stainless steel design will go with any kitchen countertop. 

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of the Zojirushi Micom Rice Cooker & Warmer. Shop for the Zojirushi Micom Rice Cooker & Warmer, as well as the full line of Zojirushi Kitchen Appliances at Abt today!
